/-- Given an open cover `{ U·µ¢ }` of `X`, and for each `U·µ¢` an open cover, we may combine these
open covers to form an open cover of `X`.  -/
@[simps J obj map]
def open_cover.bind (f : Œ† (x : ùí∞.J), open_cover (ùí∞.obj x)) : open_cover X :=
{ J := Œ£ (i : ùí∞.J), (f i).J,
